Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:09.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(319,149)}『１  折断的手指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:09.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(284,158)}２  扭曲的膝盖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:09.47,FFF,+,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(247,167)}３  掰断的手腕』
